(2, 9, '2011-02-02 08:45:39', '2011-02-02 08:45:39', 'Victory Blue is a newly established business segment of <a href="http://vicfuel.com" target="_blank">Victory Diesel</a>, a parent company specializing in alternative fuels.  Victory was founded in response to rising petrol costs and increasing environmental concerns. The company has been contributing to the reduced dependence of foreign energy sources since 2005 by promoting bio fuels as an alternative to petroleum diesel.  Victory prides itself on providing an efficient professional service and superior products with a particular emphasis on quality and value.  Victory is committed to the company\'s original mission to better the quality of life, and the introduction of Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF) is in line with the company\'s core values.', 'Company', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'company', '', '', '2014-03-20 11:34:39', '2014-03-20 16:34:39', '', 0, 'http://victoryblue.squareminc.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(4, 9, '2011-02-02 08:45:39', '2011-02-02 08:45:39', 'This is an example of a WordPress page, you could edit this to put information about yourself or your site so readers know where you are coming from. You can create as many pages like this one or sub-pages as you like and manage all of your content inside of WordPress.', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision', '', '', '2011-02-02 08:45:39', '2011-02-02 08:45:39', '', 2, 'http://victoryblue.squareminc.com/?p=4', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(6, 9, '2011-02-02 20:40:01', '2011-02-02 20:40:01', '<a href="http://dev.govictoryblue.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/smdeftruck11.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-267" title="smdeftruck1" alt="SM Def Truck" src="http://dev.govictoryblue.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/smdeftruck11.jpg" width="250" height="333" /></a>Victory Blue is a branded distributor of Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF).  DEF is a solution of urea and de-ionized water that, when injected into the exhaust stream (a process known as selective catalytic reduction, or SCR), eliminates 90% of exhaust pollutants by converting them to nitrogen and water.  Tier 2 Bin 5 emissions standards currently require all new diesel vehicles on U.S. highways to comply with stricter emissions standards set forth by the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA).  Victory Blue meets or exceeds all of the International Organization for Standardization (ISO) requirements for use in SCR systems.\r\n\r\n...', 'About DEF', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-def', '', '', '2014-03-20 11:07:42', '2014-03-20 16:07:42', '', 0, 'http://victoryblue.squareminc.com/?page_id=6', 0, 'page', '', 0),
