(77, 9, '2011-02-26 23:52:46', '2011-02-26 23:52:46', 'Victory Blue is a branded distributor of Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF).   DEF is a solution of urea and de-ionized water that when injected into  the exhaust stream (a process known as selective catalytic reduction, or  SCR) eliminates 90% of exhaust pollutants by converting them to  nitrogen and water.  Tier 2 Bin 5 emissions standards currently require  all new diesel vehicles on U.S. highways to comply with stricter  emissions standards set forth by the Environmental Protection Agency  (EPA).  Victory Blue meets or exceeds all of the International  Organization for Standardization (ISO) requirements for use in SCR  systems.', 'About DEF', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-revision-3', '', '', '2011-02-26 23:52:46', '2011-02-26 23:52:46', '', 6, 'http://victoryblue.squareminc.com/?p=77', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
