(543, 49, '2013-09-04 10:18:48', '2013-09-04 15:18:48', '<b>Victory Blue to present at North America’s leading conference for diesel emissions reduction strategy</b>\r\n\r\nVictory Blue will present at the <a href="http://www.integer-research.com/dec-usa-2013/" target="_blank">6<sup>th</sup> Diesel Emissions Conference &amp; DEF Forum USA 2013</a>, North America’s global platform for senior executives from North American and global vehicle and engine manufacturers and policy makers. The conference will take place from the 22 – 24 of October and will examine profitable and fuel efficient emissions reduction across on and off-road sectors in North America.\r\n\r\nJason Lower, Executive Vice President of Victory Blue, will speak at the three day event, which will focus on the roadmap for future regulations and technology options for heavy duty trucks, off-highway vehicles, marine vessels and light duty vehicles. It will also focus on developments in the natural gas sector. The DEF Forum will provide a comprehensive update on the industry, and discuss issues surrounding the protection of DEF quality and advancements in distribution and supply modes.\r\n\r\nMr. Lower will participate in the conference as follows:\r\n\r\n<b>Sessions:</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Day 3, 24 October</b>\r\n\r\nTime: 10.00am, Panel discussion: Future trends and challenges in the DEF market\r\n\r\nThe conference will take place at the <a href="http://www.integer-research.com/dec-usa-2013/venue/" target="_blank">Hyatt Regency Atlanta</a>.\r\n\r\nFor more information, visit <a href="http://www.integer-research.com/dec-usa-2013/" target="_blank">http://www.integer-<wbr />research.com/dec-usa-2013/</a>\r\n<h2 id="banner"><a href="http://www.integer-research.com/dec-usa-2013/"><img alt="" src="http://www.integer-research.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Web-banner2.gif" width="840" height="107" /></a></h2>', 'Victory Blue EVP Jason Lower to Speak at 6th Diesel Emissions Conference & DEF Forum', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'victory-blue-evp-jason-lower-to-speak-at-6th-diesel-emissions-conference-def-forum', '', '', '2013-09-04 10:18:48', '2013-09-04 15:18:48', '', 0, 'http://dev.govictoryblue.com/?p=543', 0, 'post', '', 0),
