(573, 49, '2013-09-13 14:25:24', '2013-09-13 19:25:24', '<b>ANNOUNCING</b>\n\nA change in hours and procedures at the Victory Blue New Orleans facility!\n\nThere are some very exciting changes occurring at Victory Blue’s New Orleans facility, including new and improved urea loading hours that are effective immediately! These new hours will make Victory Blue more available to our customers!\n<ul>\n	<li>Urea loading will now be available from 8:00 AM until 4:00 AM (the next day)!</li>\n	<li>We will cease loading from 4:00 AM to 8:00 AM each day to batch up to the tanks from the urea plant and allow the laboratory time to analyze the samples for the tanks.</li>\n	<li>We can load on weekends, with the same limitations…no loading from 4:00AM to 8:00AM.</li>\n</ul>\n<center><a href="http://dev.govictoryblue.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/schedule-of-new-hours.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-571" alt="" src="http://dev.govictoryblue.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/schedule-of-new-hours.png" width="309" height="318" /></a></center><b>Important things to note</b>:\n<ul>\n	<li>Orders must ideally be placed within 24-48 hours before they are picked up so they can be processed in time. This will also prevent delays.</li>\n	<li>The plant can only process orders during regular business hours (8:00 AM-4:00 PM).\n<ul>\n	<li> The orders that come in later in the day, after 4:00 PM will not be processed until the next day.</li>\n	<li>Please inform Victory Blue Customer Service at <a href="mailto:orders@dev.govictoryblue.com">orders@dev.govictoryblue.com</a> of any scheduling or scheduling changes.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'Victory Blue Changes Hours and Procedures at LA Facility ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '570-revision', '', '', '2013-09-13 14:25:24', '2013-09-13 19:25:24', '', 570, 'http://dev.govictoryblue.com/2013/09/13/570-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
