(762, 49, '2013-07-23 13:46:13', '2013-07-23 18:46:13', '<a href="http://dev.govictoryblue.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/smdeftruck11.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-267" title="smdeftruck1" alt="SM Def Truck" src="http://dev.govictoryblue.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/smdeftruck11.jpg" width="250" height="333" /></a>Victory Blue is a branded distributor of Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF).  DEF is a solution of urea and de-ionized water that when injected into the exhaust stream (a process known as selective catalytic reduction, or SCR) eliminates 90% of exhaust pollutants by converting them to nitrogen and water.  Tier 2 Bin 5 emissions standards currently require all new diesel vehicles on U.S. highways to comply with stricter emissions standards set forth by the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA).  Victory Blue meets or exceeds all of the International Organization for Standardization (ISO) requirements for use in SCR systems.\r\n\r\n...', 'About DEF', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '6-revision-22', '', '', '2013-07-23 13:46:13', '2013-07-23 18:46:13', '', 6, 'http://dev.govictoryblue.com/2013/07/23/6-revision-22/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
