(777, 37, '2014-10-30 14:18:22', '2014-10-30 19:18:22', '<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://dev.govictoryblue.com/">Victory Blue</a> has announced the opening of a new bulk Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF) distribution location in collaboration with <a href="http://www.csx.com/index.cfm/customers/product-transloading-and-distribution/transflo/"> CSX TRANSFLO</a>, which expands its service capabilities to Nashville, TN.\r\n\r\nIn Q3 2014, Victory Blue announced a strategic partnership with bulk commodity transloading company CSX TRANSFLO. By leveraging CSX\'s facilities, Victory has been able to serve a larger customer base.\r\n\r\n"This strategic partnership will propel us to the next level", said Thomas Paquin, President of Victory Blue. "The team at Victory Blue continues to navigate the DEF market with precision and expertise, building on an already impressive network of production and distribution sites. We continue to outperform industry growth, gain market share and customer confidence. Victory is now recognized as one of the industry\'s top producers and distributors of DEF. This is a direct result of the dedication of our entire staff to the Victory Model.  By partnering with TRANSFLO Terminal Services, we have the ability to extend the same high quality service to a much larger customer base.  We couldn\'t ask for a better partner as we look forward to continued growth."\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="NewsPostMeta">This entry was written by Rebecca Hayward of <a href="http://www.discoverdef.com/news/2014/10/30/victory-blue-extends-diesel-exhaust-fluid-%28def%29-distribution-footprint-to-nashville/">discoverdef.com</a> and posted on 30 Oct 2014</div>', 'Victory Blue extends distribution footprint to Nashville', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'victory-blue-extends-diesel-exhaust-fluid-def-distribution-footprint-to-nashville', '', '', '2014-10-30 14:19:18', '2014-10-30 19:19:18', '', 0, 'http://dev.govictoryblue.com/?p=777', 0, 'post', '', 0),
